		========================
		ROFlt - Read-Only Filter
			  README
		========================

This software is distributed under the GNU General Public License Version 3.

1. Introduction

	ROFlt or Read-Only Filter is a filter for the RedirFS Framework. It
	makes selected directories read-only. All modifying operations, like
	mkdir, unlink or create, over these directories return the EROFS error.

	For an overview of the RedirFS project, visit 

		http://www.redirfs.org

2. Installation

	See the INSTALL file.

3. Documentation

	http://www.redirfs.org/tiki-index.php?page=redirfs_doc

4. Problems & Bugs
	
